criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Clinical diagnosis of neuromyelitis optica

          -  Chinese Han nationality, gender is unlimited;

          -  Must be able to accept methylprednisolone pulse therapy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Other optic nerve diseases, such as ischemic, compressive, invasive, traumatic, toxic
             and nutritional metabolic, hereditary optic neuropathy;

          -  Visual path and central lesion on optic chiasma;

          -  Other eye diseases, such as anterior segment lesions, retinopathy, macular lesions,
             ametropia, glaucoma, etc;

          -  Non-organic visual impairment;

          -  Treated with glucocorticoid in two weeks.
